<div id="cookie-banner" class="cookie-banner" style="display: none;">
  <div class="cookie-content">
    <h5>We gebruiken cookies</h5>
    <p>We gebruiken cookies om je gebruikservaring te verbeteren. Je kunt zelf kiezen welke cookies je toelaat.</p>

    <form id="cookie-form">
      <div class="form-check">
        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="analyticsCookies" />
        <label class="form-check-label" for="analyticsCookies">
          Analytische cookies (Google Analytics)
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="form-check">
        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="externalCookies" />
        <label class="form-check-label" for="externalCookies">
          Externe content (Google Maps)
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="cookie-buttons mt-3">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Opslaan</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" id="acceptAll">Alles accepteren</button>
      </div>
    </form>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #ccc;">
  Je kunt je cookie-instellingen altijd aanpassen via de link onderaan elke pagina.
    </p>
    <a href="/cookiebeleid" target="_blank" class="cookie-link">Meer info in ons cookiebeleid</a>
  </div>
</div>
